00:00:13.250 --> 00:00:16.970
talking about is what's referred
to as the color gamut, okay?

00:00:16.970 --> 00:00:21.840
And color gamuts are just
subsets of possible colors.

00:00:21.840 --> 00:00:26.330
And here I'm showing you
three different color gamuts

00:00:26.330 --> 00:00:29.960
that have been measured or that
are just defined in a particular way.

