Notice that on the inside,
is this triangle that is

00:00:45.640 --> 00:00:51.930
a tremendous subset of that possible
set and you see it says HDTV.

00:00:51.930 --> 00:00:55.700
Turns out these are all
the colors that HDTV can make.

00:00:55.700 --> 00:00:59.300
So if you wanted to make this
really nice lush deep green,

00:00:59.300 --> 00:01:03.600
